Name:Thief
Desc:The Thief only wakes up on the first night. They must steal the role of another player and the cards will be switched around. For the rest of the game, the Thief acts as a normal Citizen. After the Thief goes back to sleep, the Host must touch the Thief's target's shoulder and wake them up - so that they are aware their role has changed.
